---
import '../styles/global.css';
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
---

<MainLayout title="关于我 - 派小站">
  <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-8">
    <!-- 页面标题 -->
    <header class="text-center mb-16">
      <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
        <div class="h-px w-12 bg-blue-600"></div>
        <span class="text-blue-600 text-sm font-black uppercase tracking-[0.3em]">About</span>
        <div class="h-px w-12 bg-blue-600"></div>
      </div>
      <h1 class="text-5xl font-black text-slate-900 tracking-tight mb-4">
        关于我
      </h1>
      <p class="text-slate-500 text-lg">
        热爱生活，充满好奇心，喜欢 coding 的创作者
      </p>
    </header>

    <!-- 个人介绍卡片 -->
    <div class="relative mb-16">
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-500/10 to-cyan-500/10 rounded-3xl blur-3xl"></div>
      <div class="relative bg-white border border-slate-100 rounded-3xl p-8 lg:p-12 shadow-xl">
        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-8 items-start">
          <!-- 头像/Logo -->
          <div class="flex-shrink-0">
            <img src="/avatar.png" alt="头像" class="w-32 h-32 rounded-2xl shadow-lg object-cover" />
          </div>

          <!-- 介绍文字 -->
          <div class="flex-1 space-y-4">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-black text-slate-900">
              你好，我是 kinass 👋
            </h2>
            <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
              这里是我的数字角落 —— <span class="text-blue-600 font-semibold">派小站</span>，记录我在生活与技术间的思考与探索。
            </p>
            <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
              我相信<span class="text-slate-900 font-semibold">活着的意义，是追寻永恒</span>。代码能让思想延续，影像能让时光停驻，音乐能让情感跨越岁月重生。我所热爱的，都是能穿越时间、留下共鸣的事物。
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- 兴趣爱好 -->
    <section class="mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-black text-slate-900 mb-8 flex items-center gap-3">
        <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-blue-500" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M4.318 6.318a4.5 4.5 0 000 6.364L12 20.364l7.682-7.682a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364-6.364L12 7.636l-1.318-1.318a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364 0z" />
        </svg>
        兴趣与热爱
      </h2>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        <!-- 编程 -->
        <div class="group relative overflow-hidden bg-white border border-slate-100 rounded-2xl p-6 hover:border-blue-500/30 hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-blue-500/5 transition-all duration-500">
          <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-24 h-24 bg-blue-50 rounded-full -translate-y-1/2 translate-x-1/2 group-hover:scale-150 transition-transform duration-500"></div>
          <div class="relative z-10">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-blue-500 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-4 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M10 20l4-16m4 4l4 4-4 4M6 16l-4-4 4-4" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">编程创作</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm leading-relaxed">
              从高中用手机写推箱子小游戏开始，就爱上了编程。不断学习，拓展知识边界，在数字世界留下自己的痕迹。
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- 音乐 -->
        <div class="group relative overflow-hidden bg-white border border-slate-100 rounded-2xl p-6 hover:border-purple-500/30 hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-purple-500/5 transition-all duration-500">
          <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-24 h-24 bg-purple-50 rounded-full -translate-y-1/2 translate-x-1/2 group-hover:scale-150 transition-transform duration-500"></div>
          <div class="relative z-10">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-purple-500 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-4 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 19V6l12-3v13M9 19c0 1.105-1.343 2-3 2s-3-.895-3-2 1.343-2 3-2 3 .895 3 2zm12-3c0 1.105-1.343 2-3 2s-3-.895-3-2 1.343-2 3-2 3 .895 3 2zM9 10l12-3" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">音乐 🎸</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm leading-relaxed">
              黄昏时分常坐在阳台上拨响吉他琴弦。那是离心最近的乐器，每一次振动都像在与心跳共鸣。
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- 摄影 -->
        <div class="group relative overflow-hidden bg-white border border-slate-100 rounded-2xl p-6 hover:border-cyan-500/30 hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-cyan-500/5 transition-all duration-500">
          <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-24 h-24 bg-cyan-50 rounded-full -translate-y-1/2 translate-x-1/2 group-hover:scale-150 transition-transform duration-500"></div>
          <div class="relative z-10">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-cyan-500 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-4 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M3 9a2 2 0 012-2h.93a2 2 0 001.664-.89l.812-1.22A2 2 0 0110.07 4h3.86a2 2 0 011.664.89l.812 1.22A2 2 0 0018.07 7H19a2 2 0 012 2v9a2 2 0 01-2 2H5a2 2 0 01-2-2V9z" />
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M15 13a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">摄影 📷</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm leading-relaxed">
              摄影让我能定格时间、留住感受。每一次按下快门，都是为生命设下一个锚点。让记忆再度发光。
              <span class="text-xs text-slate-400">（攒钱买相机中...）</span>
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- 我的信念 -->
    <section class="mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-black text-slate-900 mb-8 flex items-center gap-3">
        <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-blue-500" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M11.049 2.927c.3-.921 1.603-.921 1.902 0l1.519 4.674a1 1 0 00.95.69h4.915c.969 0 1.371 1.24.588 1.81l-3.976 2.888a1 1 0 00-.363 1.118l1.518 4.674c.3.922-.755 1.688-1.538 1.118l-3.976-2.888a1 1 0 00-1.176 0l-3.976 2.888c-.783.57-1.838-.197-1.538-1.118l1.518-4.674a1 1 0 00-.363-1.118l-3.976-2.888c-.784-.57-.38-1.81.588-1.81h4.914a1 1 0 00.951-.69l1.519-4.674z" />
        </svg>
        我的信念
      </h2>
      <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-50 to-blue-50 border border-slate-100 rounded-3xl p-8 lg:p-12">
        <blockquote class="text-xl lg:text-2xl text-slate-700 leading-relaxed text-center font-medium">
          生命终有尽头，而我相信<span class="text-blue-600 font-black">活着的意义，是追寻永恒</span>。
        </blockquote>
        <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mt-6 text-center">
          代码能让思想延续，影像能让时光停驻，音乐能让情感跨越岁月重生。<br />
          我所热爱的，都是能穿越时间、留下共鸣的事物。<br />
          在有限的生命里，去发现并创造那些永恒的美好。
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- 联系方式 -->
    <section class="mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-black text-slate-900 mb-8 flex items-center gap-3">
        <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-blue-500" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M8 12h.01M12 12h.01M16 12h.01M21 12c0 4.418-4.03 8-9 8a9.863 9.863 0 01-4.255-.949L3 20l1.395-3.72C3.512 15.042 3 13.574 3 12c0-4.418 4.03-8 9-8s9 3.582 9 8z" />
        </svg>
        期待连接
      </h2>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <!-- QQ -->
        <a
          href="tencent://message/?uin=3458651538"
          class="group relative overflow-hidden bg-white border border-slate-100 rounded-2xl p-6 hover:border-blue-500/30 hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-blue-500/5 transition-all duration-500 flex items-center gap-6"
        >
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-blue-50 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-blue-500" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
              <path d="M12 2C6.48 2 2 5.58 2 10c0 2.37 1.34 4.48 3.5 5.93l-.5 2.07 2.28-1.13C8.42 17.38 10.15 18 12 18c5.52 0 10-3.58 10-8s-4.48-8-10-8zm1 13h-2v-2h2v2zm0-4h-2V7h2v4z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 mb-1">QQ</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm">3458651538</p>
          </div>
          <svg class="absolute right-6 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-5 h-5 text-slate-300 group-hover:text-blue-500 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-all" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13.5 4.5L21 12m0 0l-7.5 7.5M21 12H3" />
          </svg>
        </a>

        <!-- GitHub -->
        <a
          href="https://github.com/kinassdc"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="group relative overflow-hidden bg-white border border-slate-100 rounded-2xl p-6 hover:border-slate-700/30 hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-slate-500/5 transition-all duration-500 flex items-center gap-6"
        >
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-slate-50 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-slate-700" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path d="M12 0c-6.626 0-12 5.373-12 12 0 5.302 3.438 9.8 8.207 11.387.599.111.793-.261.793-.577v-2.234c-3.338.726-4.033-1.416-4.033-1.416-.546-1.387-1.333-1.756-1.333-1.756-1.089-.745.083-.729.083-.729 1.205.084 1.839 1.237 1.839 1.237 1.07 1.834 2.807 1.304 3.492.997.107-.775.418-1.305.762-1.604-2.665-.305-5.467-1.334-5.467-5.931 0-1.311.469-2.381 1.236-3.221-.124-.303-.535-1.524.117-3.176 0 0 1.008-.322 3.301 1.23.957-.266 1.983-.399 3.003-.404 1.02.005 2.047.138 3.006.404 2.291-1.552 3.297-1.23 3.297-1.23.653 1.653.242 2.874.118 3.176.77.84 1.235 1.911 1.235 3.221 0 4.609-2.807 5.624-5.479 5.921.43.372.823 1.102.823 2.222v3.293c0 .319.192.694.801.576 4.765-1.589 8.199-6.086 8.199-11.386 0-6.627-5.373-12-12-12z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 mb-1">GitHub</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm">kinassdc</p>
          </div>
          <svg class="absolute right-6 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-5 h-5 text-slate-300 group-hover:text-slate-700 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-all" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M10 6H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2v-4M14 4h6m0 0v6m0-6L10 14" />
          </svg>
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- 底部语 -->
    <div class="text-center py-12 border-t border-slate-200">
      <p class="text-slate-600 text-lg leading-relaxed">
        感谢你的到访，愿我们都能在数字与现实的交汇处，<br />
        <span class="text-blue-600 font-black">找到属于自己的光</span>。
      </p>
      <div class="mt-8 flex justify-center">
        <a
          href="/"
          class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-6 py-3 bg-slate-900 text-white rounded-full text-sm font-black uppercase tracking-wider hover:bg-blue-600 transition-colors"
        >
          <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M3 12l2-2m0 0l7-7 7 7M5 10v10a1 1 0 001 1h3m10-11l2 2m-2-2v10a1 1 0 01-1 1h-3m-6 0a1 1 0 001-1v-4a1 1 0 011-1h2a1 1 0 011 1v4a1 1 0 001 1m-6 0h6" />
          </svg>
          返回首页
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</MainLayout>
